{"lemma":"ذِبْحَةُ","slug":"ذِبْحَةُ","root":"ذ.ب.ح","root_slug":"ذ-ب-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ب-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13682","n13683","n13684","n13685"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"angina"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ðab.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13682","headword_ar":"ذُبْحَةٌ","root":"*bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ubaHapN","text_ar":"ذُبَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13683","headword_ar":"ذِبْحَةٌ","root":"*bH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aboH","text_ar":"ذَبْح"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slaughter, such as is described in the first paragraph of this art."},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.)       -A2-  See also what here next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13684","headword_ar":"ذُبَحَةٌ","root":"*bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uboHahN","text_ar":"ذُبْحَهٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, A, K,) but this latter, which is used by the vulgar, was unknown to AZ, (S,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ubaAHN","text_ar":"ذُبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ibaHapN","text_ar":"ذِبَحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iboHapN","text_ar":"ذِبْحَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ibaAHN","text_ar":"ذِبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iboHN","text_ar":"ذِبْحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A disease,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, A,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (AZ, T, S, A, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which sometimes kills:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blood which chokes and kills:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ulcer that comes forth in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a man, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iy^obap","text_ar":"ذِيْبَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that attacks the ass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an ulcer that appears in that part, obstructing it, and stopping the breath, and killing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*atohu","text_ar":"اَخَذَتْهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~ubaHapu","text_ar":"الذُّبَحَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*bHp","text_ar":"ذبحة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attacked him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlT~amaEu *ubaAHN","text_ar":"الطَّمَعُ ذُبَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Covetousness is"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disease in the fauces:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a poisonous plant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna *`lika mivola Al*~ubaHapi EalaY Aln~aHori","text_ar":"كَانَ ذٰلِكَ مِثْلَ الذُّبَحَةِ عَلَى النَّحْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That was like the disease called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*bHp","text_ar":"ذبحة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the uppermost part of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: a prov., applied to the case of a man whom one imagines to be a sincere friend, and who proves to be an evident enemy: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna mivola Al*~ubaHapi Alx","text_ar":"كَانَ مِثْلَ الذُّبَحَةِ الخ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*bHp","text_ar":"ذبحة"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., a disease in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haloq","text_ar":"حَلْق"},{"kind":"text","text":", which does not quit the patient externally, and hurts him internally: said by him to whom you complain of one whom you imagined to be a sincere friend, and whose affection was outward, when his deceit has become manifest. (Meyd.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dubaHapN","text_ar":"دُبَحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also the n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ubaHN","text_ar":"ذُبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (Fr, AHn.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","S","A","K","As","TA","T","ISh"]},{"entry_id":"n13685","headword_ar":"ذِبَحَةٌ","root":"*bH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph.       -A2-  It is also the n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ibaHN","text_ar":"ذِبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uabaHN","text_ar":"ذَُبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Fr, AHn.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}